text: Just had Kelvin Printing to print sets of a boardgame I created for a client and the results were delightful. Ze Ying was responsive, enthusiastic, professional, and the delivery was timely. Thank you!

Worked with Zeying for a few jobs already, they always deliver good results, be it brochures or books, quality is always top notch, inexpensive, and punctual delivery! Will definitely work with them again!
Amazing service, speedy delivery and delivered with care. If you are looking for a reliable printing and delivery service, consider this.

Ordered for a delivery of a calender and had a very tight dateline of 2days inclusive of editing my design and printing it. They've exceeded beyond my expectations and produced the item with quality and with super efficient delivery system. The PIC Ms Ze Ying was kind and extremely thoughtful too that makes the whole process so much more smoother. Great job definitely will return again for more in the future!
Discovered a new printing gem, love the prompt replies and service!
